race.comment: ARCTIC FOX (11) has missed the frame in two runs this time in but both occasions has drawn off the track. Fitter again and going better than it looks. Has finally drawn a gate and gets chance to break through. I HAD A DREAM (1) is also fitter for two runs in, the latest running on hard to place, finishing in front of ARCTIC FOX who was seventh. Also looks ready to fire now but will need some luck from the wide draw. Think they can fight this out. GLIMMERINTHEDUST (5) went out big odds last time but ran a much better race on speed. That was a career best but still has upside and off the low draw will give a sight again. THROW ME A KISS (8) was tested to a mile before a spell but has run some good races over this trip. Has a nice draw and should run well fresh. MISS WEENI (12) wasn't far from the winner and split ARCTIC FOX and I HAD A DREAM last time in fifth. Rates well on that effort.
